From 0287362e846643632c8779850b5c62cad36614da Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 1 May 2026 09:53:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Add dispatch slip feature to harvests module

- New dispatchSlipService.ts handles create/update/fulfill/cancel
- Auto-creates harvest when stock is available on slip creation
- Saves as pending when stock is insufficient
- Harvest page now has Harvest Log / Dispatch Slips tabs
- Pending slips can be edited, fulfilled manually, or cancelled
- Fulfilled slips support printable dispatch slip (shared print template)
- Badge on tab shows count of pending slips

